snippet.title: Chris Noth Talks ‘Sad And Uncomfortable’ Feud Between Sarah Jessica Parker And Kim Cattrall
snippet.description:
In a new interview with The Guardian, "Sex and the City" star Chris Noth weighs in on the "sad and uncomfortable" feud between Sarah Jessica Parker and Kim Cattrall. Plus, executive producer Michael Patrick King reveals how Cattrall's character Samantha Jones will be written out of the upcoming sequel "And Just Like That”. Morgan Hoffman and Sangita Patel react on ET Canada Live.
#ChristNoth #SarahJessicaParker #KimCattrall
